    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly a little sad to see this one go, but it\u2019s time for a new home! This car has been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in truly pristine, showroom-level condition. It\u2019s been babied since day one, always garage-kept and meticulously cared for\u2014you seriously won\u2019t find a single flaw. It looks and drives just like it\u2019s brand new! If you\u2019re looking for perfection on wheels, you\u2019ve found it. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to see it go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have!",
      "price": 45900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
