    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m listing my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total showstopper! This car is in truly pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It's been meticulously cared for, garage-kept, and treated like royalty. You won't find a single scratch or speck of dust out of place. It drives like a dream and still has that wonderful new-car smell! I'm so excited for someone new to get behind the wheel and enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 43500.0,
