    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade FD3S Mazda RX-7, showcasing an impeccable 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine. This specimen maintains factory-spec compression and exhibits no signs of thermal fatigue or vacuum manifold degradation. The power delivery is seamless through the 5-speed manual gearbox, paired with a perfectly calibrated Torsen limited-slip differential. The chassis retains its legendary 50/50 weight distribution, supported by an untouched four-wheel double-wishbone suspension system. The exterior retains its original high-gloss finish with zero panel gap irregularities, while the cockpit-oriented interior remains free of UV damage or bolster wear. A mechanically pristine example of 90s JDM engineering.",
